{"id": "art-294", "label": "Art. 294", "title": "Art. 294", "slug": "art-294", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 294 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>Pe data <span\nclass=SpellE>într&#259;rii</span> în vigoare a prezentei <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>legi</i> se abrog&#259; prevederile art. </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>77</span><span style='color:black'>-</span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>220</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>236</span><span style='color:black'> din </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul comercial</span><sup><span style='color:black'>8</span></sup><span\nstyle='color:black'>), prevederile referitoare la întreprinderile mici <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> la <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;iile</span> cu\nscop lucrativ, cu personalitate juridic&#259;, din Decretul-<i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i> nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>54/1990</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind organizarea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>desf&#259;&#351;urarea</span> unor <span class=SpellE>activit&#259;&#355;i</span>\neconomice pe baza liberei <span class=SpellE>ini&#355;iative</span>, Decretul\nnr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>424/1972</span><span style='color:black'>\nprivind constituirea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ionarea</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> mixte în România, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>15</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>28 alin. 1</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>33</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>35 alin. 2 <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 3</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, Decretul-<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>\nnr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>96/1990</span><span style='color:black'>\nprivind unele m&#259;suri pentru atragerea <span class=SpellE>investi&#355;iei</span>\nde capital str&#259;in în România.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>-****-</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><sup><span style='color:black'>1</span></sup><span\nstyle='color:black'>) Republicat&#259; în temeiul art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>XII</span><span style='color:black'> din titlul II al <span\nclass=SpellE>c&#259;r&#355;ii</span> a II-a din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>161/2003</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind unele m&#259;suri pentru asigurarea <span\nclass=SpellE>transparen&#355;ei</span> în exercitarea <span class=SpellE>demnit&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\npublice, a <span class=SpellE>func&#355;iilor</span> publice <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în mediul de afaceri, prevenirea <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>sanc&#355;ionarea</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>corup&#355;iei</span>, publicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al\nRomâniei, Partea I, nr. 279 din 21 aprilie 2003, cu modific&#259;rile\nulterioare, dându-se textelor o nou&#259; numerotare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'><span style='color:black'>Legea</span></i><span\nstyle='color:black'> nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>31/1990</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> a mai fost republicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al\nRomâniei, Partea I, nr. 33 din 29 ianuarie 1998, iar ulterior a fost\nmodificat&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> completat&#259; prin:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>- <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;a</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>16/1998</span><span style='color:black'> pentru\nprorogarea termenului prev&#259;zut la art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>VI\nalin. 1</span><span style='color:black'> din <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;a</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>32/1997</span><span style='color:black'> pentru\nmodificarea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> completarea <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>Legii</i> nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>31/1990</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\ncomerciale, publicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea I, nr. 359\ndin 22 septembrie 1998, aprobat&#259; prin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i>\nnr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>237/1998</span><span style='color:black'>,\npublicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea I, nr. 477 din 11\ndecembrie 1998;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>- <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>99/1999</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind unele m&#259;suri pentru accelerarea reformei\neconomice, publicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea I, nr. 236\ndin 27 mai 1999, cu modific&#259;rile ulterioare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>- <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;a</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>75/1999</span><span style='color:black'> privind\nactivitatea de audit financiar, republicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al\nRomâniei, Partea I, nr. 598 din 22 august 2003, cu modific&#259;rile\nulterioare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>- Legea nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>127/2000</span><span style='color:black'> pentru\nmodificarea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> completarea art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>156</span><span style='color:black'> din <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>31/1990</span><span style='color:black'> privind <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\ncomerciale, publicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea I, nr. 345\ndin 25 iulie 2000;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>- <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;a</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>76/2001</span><span style='color:black'> privind\nsimplificarea unor <span class=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;i</span>\nadministrative pentru înregistrarea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nautorizarea <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ion&#259;rii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>comercian&#355;ilor</span>, republicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial\nal României, Partea I, nr. 413 din 14 iunie 2002, cu modific&#259;rile <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile ulterioare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>- <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>314/2001</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> pentru reglementarea <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iei</span>\nunor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> comerciale, publicat&#259;\nîn Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea I, nr. 338 din 26 iunie 2001, cu\nmodific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile\nulterioare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>- <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;a</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>102/2002</span><span style='color:black'> privind unele\nm&#259;suri pentru stimularea cererii de atribuire a <span class=SpellE>folosin&#355;ei</span>\ngratuite <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a <span class=SpellE>investi&#355;iilor</span>\nîn imobilele ce fac obiectul <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;ei</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>168/2001</span><span style='color:black'> privind punerea\nîn valoare a <span class=SpellE>construc&#355;iilor</span> zootehnice\ndezafectate, destinate <span class=SpellE>cre&#351;terii</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>îngr&#259;&#351;&#259;rii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nexploat&#259;rii animalelor, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a\nfabricilor de <span class=SpellE>nutre&#355;uri</span> combinate dezafectate,\npublicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea I, nr. 673 din 11\nseptembrie 2002, aprobat&#259; cu modific&#259;ri <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncomplet&#259;ri prin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>78/2003</span><span style='color:black'>, publicat&#259;\nîn Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea I, nr. 194 din 26 martie 2003, cu\nmodific&#259;rile ulterioare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>- <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>161/2003</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind unele m&#259;suri pentru asigurarea <span\nclass=SpellE>transparen&#355;ei</span> în exercitarea <span class=SpellE>demnit&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\npublice, a <span class=SpellE>func&#355;iilor</span> publice <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în mediul de afaceri, prevenirea <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>sanc&#355;ionarea</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>corup&#355;iei</span>, cu modific&#259;rile ulterioare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>- Legea nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>297/2004</span><span style='color:black'> privind <span\nclass=SpellE>pia&#355;a</span> de capital, publicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial\nal României, Partea I, nr. 571 din 29 iunie 2004.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><sup><span style='color:black'>2</span></sup><span\nstyle='color:black'>) <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;a</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>28/2002</span><span style='color:black'> privind valorile\nmobiliare, serviciile de <span class=SpellE>investi&#355;ii</span> financiare <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>pie&#355;ele</span> reglementate\na fost abrogat&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> înlocuit&#259; prin <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>297/2004</span><span style='color:black'> privind <span class=SpellE>pia&#355;a</span>\nde capital, publicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea I, nr. 571\ndin 29 iunie 2004.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><sup><span style='color:black'>3</span></sup><span\nstyle='color:black'>) Potrivit art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>V</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> din <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;a</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>32/1997</span><span style='color:black'> pentru\nmodificarea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> completarea <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>Legii</i> nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>31/1990</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\ncomerciale, aprobat&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> modificat&#259;\nprin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>195/1997</span><span style='color:black'>, <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span> acestui alineat nu se aplic&#259;\nfilialelor f&#259;r&#259; personalitate juridic&#259; <span class=SpellE>înfiin&#355;ate</span>\npân&#259; la data intr&#259;rii în vigoare a <span class=SpellE>ordonan&#355;ei</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>Se recomand&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> care au <span class=SpellE>înfiin&#355;at</span>\n<span class=SpellE>unit&#259;&#355;i</span> f&#259;r&#259; personalitate\njuridic&#259; s&#259; modifice denumirea de filial&#259; dat&#259; acestora.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><sup><span style='color:black'>4</span></sup><span\nstyle='color:black'>) A se vedea nota de la art. </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>35</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><sup><span style='color:black'>5</span></sup><span\nstyle='color:black'>) <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>52/1994</span><span style='color:black'> privind valorile\nmobiliare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> bursele de valori a fost\nabrogat&#259; prin <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;a</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>28/2002</span><span style='color:black'>, aceasta fiind,\nde asemenea, abrogat&#259; prin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i>\nnr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>297/2004</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><sup><span style='color:black'>6</span></sup><span\nstyle='color:black'>) A se vedea nota de la art. </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>168</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><sup><span style='color:black'>7</span></sup><span\nstyle='color:black'>) Potrivit art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>III</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> din <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;a</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>32/1997</span><span style='color:black'>, aprobat&#259;\ncu modific&#259;ri prin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>195/1997</span><span style='color:black'>, <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> comerciale reglementate prin <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legi</i> speciale r&#259;mân supuse <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> acelor\n<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legi</i>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><sup><span style='color:black'>8</span></sup><span\nstyle='color:black'>) Potrivit art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>IX</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> din <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;a</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>32/1997</span><span style='color:black'>, aprobat&#259;\ncu modific&#259;ri prin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>195/1997</span><span style='color:black'>, pe data\nintr&#259;rii în vigoare a acestei <span class=SpellE>ordonan&#355;e</span> (28\niulie 1997) se abrog&#259; art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>237</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>-</span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>250</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>264</span><span style='color:black'>-</span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>269</span><span style='color:black'> din </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul comercial</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>Publicat în Monitorul Oficial cu\nnum&#259;rul 1066 din data de 17 noiembrie 2004</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) <span class=SpellE>Entit&#259;&#355;ile</span>\ncare au statutul de sucursal&#259;, dar se numesc filiale, <span class=SpellE>înfiin&#355;ate</span>\nînainte de intrarea în vigoare a <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;ei</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> a Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>32/1997</span><span style='color:black'> pentru\nmodificarea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> completarea <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>Legii</i> nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>31/1990</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\ncomerciale, vor proceda la precizarea statutului lor juridic <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> la realizarea <span class=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nlegale pentru publicitate corespunz&#259;toare acestui statut, în termen de 3\nluni de la intrarea în vigoare a prezentei <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legi</i>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>În cazul unei înc&#259;lc&#259;ri a\nprevederilor alin. (1), art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>44</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>46</span><span style='color:black'> din <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>26/1990</span><span style='color:black'> privind registrul <span\nclass=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>, republicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile ulterioare, devin aplicabile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>De la data de 1 ianuarie 2007, <span\nclass=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span> financiare anuale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ndocumentele anexate acestora, prev&#259;zute la art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>185 alin. (1)</span><span style='color:black'> din Legea\nnr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>31/1990</span><span style='color:black'>\nprivind <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> comerciale,\nrepublicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncomplet&#259;rile ulterioare, modificate potrivit prezentei <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legi</i>, vor fi depuse numai la oficiul\nregistrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>În termen de 9 luni de la data\nintr&#259;rii în vigoare a prezentei <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legi</i>,\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\nvor proceda la efectuarea <span class=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nnecesare îndeplinirii <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute la art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>137 alin. (2)</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, art. 138<sup>1</sup>, art. 140<sup>1</sup> alin. (3) <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>143 alin.\n(4)</span><span style='color:black'> din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i>\nnr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>31/1990</span><span style='color:black'>,\nrepublicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncomplet&#259;rile ulterioare.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) <span class=SpellE>Societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> înregistrate în registrul <span\nclass=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> la data intr&#259;rii în vigoare a\nprezentei <span class=SpellE>ordonan&#355;e</span> de <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span>\nsunt obligate a efectua demersurile necesare îndeplinirii <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute la art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>137 alin. (1) <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 2</span><span style='color:black'>, art. 137<sup>1</sup>\nalin. (3), art. 138<sup>1</sup>, art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>143</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> din Legea nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>31/1990</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\ncomerciale, republicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncomplet&#259;rile ulterioare, inclusiv cele prev&#259;zute în prezenta <span\nclass=SpellE>ordonan&#355;&#259;</span> de <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span>,\nîn termen de 6 luni de la intrarea în vigoare a acesteia. Pân&#259; la finalizarea\nacestor demersuri, societatea poate <span class=SpellE>func&#355;iona</span> cu\nstructura de administrare existent&#259; la data intr&#259;rii în vigoare a\nprezentei <span class=SpellE>ordonan&#355;e</span> de <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>Prin derogare de la prevederile art.\n</span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>56</span><span style='color:black'> din\nLegea nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>53/2003</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> - </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul muncii</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, cu modific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncomplet&#259;rile ulterioare, contractele de munc&#259; ale\nadministratorilor/directorilor, încheiate pentru îndeplinirea mandatului de\nadministrator/director înainte de intrarea în vigoare a prezentei <span\nclass=SpellE>ordonan&#355;e</span> de <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span>,\nînceteaz&#259; de drept la data intr&#259;rii în vigoare a <span class=SpellE>ordonan&#355;ei</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> sau, în cazul în care mandatul a\nfost acceptat ulterior intr&#259;rii în vigoare a prezentei <span class=SpellE>ordonan&#355;e</span>,\nde la data accept&#259;rii mandatului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) În tot cuprinsul <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>, sintagma &quot;societate\ncomercial&#259;&quot; sau, dup&#259; caz, &quot;<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\ncomerciale&quot; se <span class=SpellE>înlocuie&#351;te</span> cu termenul\n&quot;societate&quot; sau, dup&#259; caz, &quot;<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>&quot;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n\n\n</div>\n<script>\n    // PARTEA 1: SCRIPTUL DE CĂUTARE (versiune corectată și finală cu normalizare)\n    const articlesIndex = [];\n    let currentlyHighlightedArticleElement = null;\n    let currentlyActiveSearchResultLink = null;\n    const activeArticleClassName = 'article-active-highlight-minimal';\n\n    const styleSheetSearch = document.createElement(\"style\");\n    styleSheetSearch.type = \"text/css\";\n    styleSheetSearch.innerText = `\n        .${activeArticleClassName} { \n            background-color: #e6f7ff !important; /* Un fundal albastru foarte deschis, subtil */\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;\n        }\n        /* Stilurile pentru #customSearchContainer ar trebui să fie în HTML-ul interfeței de căutare, nu aici,\n           dar le las comentate dacă se dorește adăugarea lor dinamică, deși nu e recomandat pentru stiluri statice.\n        #customSearchContainer { \n            padding: 15px; \n            background-color: #f0f0f0; \n            border-bottom: 1px solid #dcdcdc; \n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        */\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel a { \n            display: block; padding: 10px 12px; text-decoration: none; \n            color: #0056b3; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; \n            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;\n        }\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel a:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel a:hover { background-color: #f0f8ff; }\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel a.active-result-link { \n            background-color: #d4ebf7; font-weight: bold; color: #004085;\n        }\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel a small { \n            color: #495057; display: block; margin-top: 4px; \n            font-size: 0.85em; line-height: 1.3;\n        }\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel .no-results {\n            padding: 15px; color: #6c757d; font-style: italic;\n        }\n    `;\n    document.head.appendChild(styleSheetSearch);\n\n    function normalizeText(text) {\n        if (typeof text !== 'string') return '';\n        text = text.toLowerCase();\n        text = text.replace(/ă/g, 'a').replace(/â/g, 'a').replace(/î/g, 'i').replace(/ș/g, 's').replace(/ş/g, 's').replace(/ț/g, 't').replace(/ţ/g, 't');\n        return text;\n    }\n\n    function isPotentiallyArticleTitle(text) {\n        return /^(Art\\.|Articolul)\\s*\\d+/i.test(text.trim().substring(0, 25));\n    }\n\n    function getArticleTitleAndNumber(text) {\n        const match = text.trim().match(/^(Art\\.|Articolul)\\s*(\\d+)\\s*[:\\-\\s]*(.*)/i);\n        if (match) {\n            const num = match[2];\n            let title = match[3] || \"\";\n            title = title.replace(/^\\s*\\(\\d+\\)/, '').trim();\n            const displayTitleFragment = title.length > 80 ? title.substring(0, 77) + \"...\" : title;\n            return { \n                number: num, \n                titleFragment: displayTitleFragment, \n                // CORECTAT AICI: Folosim template literals corect\n                fullDeclaration: `Art. ${num}${displayTitleFragment ? (': ' + displayTitleFragment) : ''}` \n            };\n        }\n        const fallbackTitle = text.length > 80 ? text.substring(0, 77) + \"...\" : text;\n        return { number: null, titleFragment: fallbackTitle, fullDeclaration: fallbackTitle };\n    }\n    \n    function isMajorHeading(text) {\n        const upperText = text.trim().toUpperCase();\n        if (upperText.length > 60) return false; \n        return upperText.startsWith(\"TITLUL\") || \n               upperText.startsWith(\"CAPITOLUL\") ||\n               upperText.startsWith(\"SECŢIUNEA\") || \n               upperText.startsWith(\"SECȚIUNEA\") || \n               upperText.startsWith(\"CARTEA\");\n    }\n\n    function buildArticlesIndex() {\n        articlesIndex.length = 0; \n        const paragraphs = document.body.getElementsByTagName('p');\n        let currentArticleData = null;\n        let articleGlobalIndex = 0;\n\n        for (let i = 0; i < paragraphs.length; i++) {\n            const pElement = paragraphs[i];\n            if (pElement.offsetParent === null && !(pElement.offsetWidth > 0 || pElement.offsetHeight > 0)) {\n                if (!pElement.textContent.trim() && pElement.innerHTML.toLowerCase().includes(\"&nbsp;\")) {\n                    continue;\n                }\n            }\n            const pTextOriginal = (pElement.textContent || pElement.innerText || \"\").trim();\n            if (!pTextOriginal) continue; \n\n            if (isPotentiallyArticleTitle(pTextOriginal)) {\n                if (currentArticleData) { articlesIndex.push(currentArticleData); }\n                articleGlobalIndex++;\n                const uniqueId = `article-auto-${articleGlobalIndex}`;\n                pElement.id = uniqueId;\n                const titleInfo = getArticleTitleAndNumber(pTextOriginal);\n                currentArticleData = {\n                    id: uniqueId, titleElement: pElement,\n                    displayTitle: titleInfo.fullDeclaration, articleNumber: titleInfo.number,\n                    contentParagraphsElements: [pElement], fullTextContent: pTextOriginal,\n                    normalizedFullTextContent: normalizeText(pTextOriginal)\n                };\n            } else if (currentArticleData) { \n                if (isMajorHeading(pTextOriginal)) { \n                    articlesIndex.push(currentArticleData); currentArticleData = null; \n                } else {\n                    currentArticleData.contentParagraphsElements.push(pElement);\n                    currentArticleData.fullTextContent += \"\\n\" + pTextOriginal;\n                    currentArticleData.normalizedFullTextContent += \"\\n\" + normalizeText(pTextOriginal);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        if (currentArticleData) { articlesIndex.push(currentArticleData); }\n    }\n\n    function highlightTermInSnippet(snippet, termToHighlight) {\n        if (!snippet || !termToHighlight || termToHighlight.length === 0) return snippet;\n        const escapedTerm = termToHighlight.replace(/[.*+?^${}()|[\\]\\\\]/g, '\\\\$&');\n        try {\n            const regex = new RegExp(`(${escapedTerm})`, 'gi');\n            return snippet.replace(regex, '<mark>$1</mark>');\n        } catch (e) { \n            // console.error(\"Regex error in highlightTermInSnippet:\", e); // Opțional pentru debugging\n            return snippet; \n        }\n    }\n\n    function executeArticleSearch() {\n        if (articlesIndex.length === 0) { buildArticlesIndex(); }\n        const rawSearchTerm = document.getElementById('articleSearchInput').value.trim();\n        const normalizedSearchTerm = normalizeText(rawSearchTerm);\n        const resultsPanel = document.getElementById('articleSearchResultsPanel');\n        resultsPanel.innerHTML = ''; \n        removeCurrentHighlight();\n        if (currentlyActiveSearchResultLink) {\n            currentlyActiveSearchResultLink.classList.remove('active-result-link');\n            currentlyActiveSearchResultLink = null;\n        }\n        if (!rawSearchTerm) {\n            resultsPanel.innerHTML = '\n<p class=\"no-results\">Introduceți un termen de căutare.</p>\n'; return;\n        }\n        const searchResults = [];\n        const isSearchingForSpecificArticleNumberMatch = rawSearchTerm.match(/^(art\\.|articolul)\\s*(\\d+)$/i);\n        const specificArticleNumberToSearch = isSearchingForSpecificArticleNumberMatch ? isSearchingForSpecificArticleNumberMatch[2] : null;\n\n        articlesIndex.forEach(article => {\n            let matchFound = false; \n            let snippetForDisplay = \"\"; // Aici vom stoca fragmentul relevant pentru afișare\n\n            if (specificArticleNumberToSearch) {\n                if (article.articleNumber === specificArticleNumberToSearch) {\n                    matchFound = true;\n                    // Pentru potrivire exactă de articol, afișăm începutul conținutului său\n                    snippetForDisplay = article.fullTextContent.substring(0, 150) + (article.fullTextContent.length > 150 ? \"...\" : \"\");\n                    snippetForDisplay = highlightTermInSnippet(snippetForDisplay, rawSearchTerm); \n                }\n            } else {\n                const normalizedArticleFullText = article.normalizedFullTextContent;\n                const normalizedDisplayTitle = normalizeText(article.displayTitle); \n                let termFoundInTitle = normalizedDisplayTitle.includes(normalizedSearchTerm);\n                let termFoundInContent = !termFoundInTitle && normalizedArticleFullText.includes(normalizedSearchTerm);\n\n                if (termFoundInTitle) {\n                    matchFound = true;\n                    // Dacă s-a găsit în titlu, snippet-ul poate fi o parte mai relevantă a conținutului\n                    const firstMatchIndexInNormalized = normalizedDisplayTitle.indexOf(normalizedSearchTerm); \n                    const searchWindowStart = Math.max(0, firstMatchIndexInNormalized - 30); \n                    const searchWindowEnd = Math.min(article.fullTextContent.length, firstMatchIndexInNormalized + normalizedSearchTerm.length + 70); \n                    snippetForDisplay = \"...\" + article.fullTextContent.substring(searchWindowStart, searchWindowEnd) + \"...\";\n                    snippetForDisplay = highlightTermInSnippet(snippetForDisplay, rawSearchTerm);\n\n                } else if (termFoundInContent) {\n                    matchFound = true;\n                    const firstMatchIndexInNormalized = normalizedArticleFullText.indexOf(normalizedSearchTerm);\n                    const searchWindowStart = Math.max(0, firstMatchIndexInNormalized - 30);\n                    const searchWindowEnd = Math.min(article.fullTextContent.length, firstMatchIndexInNormalized + normalizedSearchTerm.length + 70);\n                    snippetForDisplay = \"...\" + article.fullTextContent.substring(searchWindowStart, searchWindowEnd) + \"...\";\n                    snippetForDisplay = highlightTermInSnippet(snippetForDisplay, rawSearchTerm);\n                }\n            }\n            if (matchFound) { searchResults.push({ article: article, snippet: snippetForDisplay }); }\n        });\n\n        if (searchResults.length > 0) {\n            searchResults.forEach(result => {\n                const link = document.createElement('a');\n                link.href = `#${result.article.id}`; \n                // CORECTAT AICI: Folosim template literals corect și afișăm titlul + snippet-ul\n                link.innerHTML = `<strong>${result.article.displayTitle}</strong><br><small>${result.snippet}</small>`;\n                \n                link.onclick = function(e) {\n                    e.preventDefault();\n                    if (currentlyActiveSearchResultLink) { currentlyActiveSearchResultLink.classList.remove('active-result-link'); }\n                    link.classList.add('active-result-link'); currentlyActiveSearchResultLink = link;\n                    scrollToArticleAndHighlight(result.article.id);\n                };\n                resultsPanel.appendChild(link);\n            });\n        } else { resultsPanel.innerHTML = '\n<p class=\"no-results\">Niciun articol găsit.</p>\n'; }\n    }\n    \n    function removeCurrentHighlight() {\n        if (currentlyHighlightedArticleElement) {\n            currentlyHighlightedArticleElement.classList.remove(activeArticleClassName);\n            currentlyHighlightedArticleElement = null;\n        }\n    }\n\n    function scrollToArticleAndHighlight(elementId) {\n        removeCurrentHighlight(); \n        const targetElement = document.getElementById(elementId);\n        if (targetElement) {\n             targetElement.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });\n            setTimeout(() => {\n                targetElement.classList.add(activeArticleClassName);\n                currentlyHighlightedArticleElement = targetElement;\n            }, 300); \n        }\n    }\n\n    function clearArticleSearch() {\n        document.getElementById('articleSearchInput').value = '';\n        document.getElementById('articleSearchResultsPanel').innerHTML = '';\n        removeCurrentHighlight();\n        if (currentlyActiveSearchResultLink) {\n            currentlyActiveSearchResultLink.classList.remove('active-result-link');\n            currentlyActiveSearchResultLink = null;\n        }\n    }\n\n    document.getElementById('articleSearchInput').addEventListener('keypress', function(event) {\n        if (event.key === 'Enter') { executeArticleSearch(); }\n    });\n\n    window.addEventListener('load', function() { /* buildArticlesIndex(); // Opțional */ });\n</script>\n\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"Legislation\",\n  \"name\": \"legea societatilor-republicare (Text Integral cu Căutare)\", // Adaptați\n  \"description\": \"Textul integral și actualizat al legea societatilor-republicare, cu funcție de căutare avansată pentru articole.\", // Adaptați\n  \"url\": \"https://www.legeaaplicata.ro/legislatie/legea societatilor-republicare.html\", // Adaptați\n  \"inLanguage\": \"ro\",\n  \"provider\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"LegeaAplicata.ro\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.legeaaplicata.ro\"\n  },\n  \"datePublished\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\", // Adaptați: Data publicării acestei pagini web\n  \"mainEntityOfPage\": {\n     \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n     \"@id\": \"https://www.legeaaplicata.ro/legislatie/legea societatilor-republicare.html\" // Adaptați\n  }\n}\n</script>\n</body>\n\n</html>\n"}